title: Bright Corner Unit, Wood Floors & Walk-In Closet - 2 Weeks Free
posting_body: ['Charming First Hill 2bed Corner Unit -2', 'Weeks Free', 'Property Address', '1400 BOREN AVE UNIT 305 | SEATTLE, WA 98101', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Oxford Crest Apartments - Seattle Property Management Associates', 'Description', 'The Oxford Crest apartments were built in 1929 and still maintains much of its Old World charm.', 'It is located near Virginia Mason, Swedish and Harborview hospitals.', 'There is a plethora of shops, bars and restaurants within walking distance as well as many entertainment attractions that can be found on Capitol Hill.', 'Enjoy the convenience of having a large and enclosed outside dog run on property where Fido can fetch and play.', 'Unit 305 is situated on the Southwest corner which faces Boren Ave and Union Street.', 'This spacious 2 bedroom unit receives great natural light throughout the day.', 'There are hardwood floors throughout, new vinyl in the kitchen and bathroom, a walk-in closet off the bedroom and a cozy L-shaped kitchen.', 'At the time of application, we require payment of the $25 application fee per person and a $500 deposit that is then applied to the refundable security deposit upon approval.', 'There is a $75 monthly utility for water/sewer/garbage per person.', 'For more information or to schedule a viewing, please contact us at', 'show contact info', 'Amenities', 'Controlled Access', 'elevator', 'Central Court Yard', 'small dogs welcome', 'Laundry Room', 'Near Transportation', 'vintage building', 'Wood Floors', 'walk-in closet', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 900', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,995.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,000.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
